ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectNo. 115 - (NB) Provincial Emergencies Financial Assistance Order
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 115 - which authorizes the federal government to provide financial assistance to the province of MANITOBA with respect to damages that occurred from March 24, 2009 to May 21, 2009, in communities nearby the Red River Basin, as well as the Pembina, Assiniboine and Souris Rivers.
